The paper discusses the use of massive MIMO architectures for secure communication, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of low complexity architectures, which could fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY).
